short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A web browser extension to provide a unified search of Irish dictionaries and glossaries

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A web browser extension that provides a unified search of sources from Teanglann.ie, Potafocal.com and Tearma.ie, all in one single page

Is síneadh é Foclóir a chuireann cuardach comhaontaithe ar fáil ar fhoinsí ó Teanglann.ie, Potafocal.com, Tearma.ie agus Gaois.ie in aon leathanach amháin.

Brú an cnaipe chun an leathanach a oscailt, roghnaigh na foinsí a theastaíonn uait agus cuardaigh focal.
